Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.95,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,那块手表是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.64,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,もしかして...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.64,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,难道是...
